\binom{n}{n_1}\binom{n-n_1}{n_2}\binom{n-n_1-n_2}{n_3}\cdots\binom{n-n_1-n_2-\dots-n_{k-1}}{n_k}
$$ equals the following expression $$
\frac{n!}{n_1!n_2!n_3!\cdots n_k!}
